  "title": "Natural Sounds - Grand Canyon National Park (U.S. National Park Service)",
  "html": "<body class=\"ParkSite\"><span aria-label=\"Top of page\" id=\"__topdoc__\" role=\"navigation\"></span>\n\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n<div id=\"beforeSkipLinks\" tabindex=\"-1\"></div>\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n<div class=\"GlobalHeader usaGlobalHeader\" role=\"banner\">\n\n</div>\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<div aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-labelledby=\"exitModalLabel\" class=\"modal refreshableModal\" id=\"myModal\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"modal-dialog\">\n<div class=\"modal-content\">\n<div class=\"modal-header\">\n<h2 class=\"modal-title visually-hidden\" id=\"exitModalLabel\">Exiting nps.gov</h2>\n<button aria-label=\"Close\" class=\"btn-close\" data-bs-dismiss=\"modal\" type=\"button\"></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"modal-body\"></div>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Schedule\" id=\"cs_control_481716\"><div id=\"CS_Element_BannerContainer\" title=\"\"><div class=\"cs_GridRow\" id=\"gridRow_1_1_481716\"><div class=\"cs_GridColumn\" id=\"gridCol_1_1_1_1_481716\"><div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_CustomCF\" id=\"cs_control_830326\"><div id=\"CS_CCF_1962738_830326\">\n\n</div></div><div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_CustomCF\" id=\"cs_control_481855\"><div id=\"CS_CCF_1962738_481855\"> </div></div></div></div></div></div>\n<div id=\"Park-header\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"pull-left\">\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n\n</div>\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div aria-label=\"Alerts Notification\" class=\"AlertsNotification\" data-site-code=\"grca\" id=\"AlertsNotification\" role=\"dialog\">\n<div aria-live=\"polite\" class=\"AlertsNotification__Status visually-hidden\" role=\"status\">Loading alerts</div>\n<div class=\"collapse\">\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__Panel\">\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__Header\">\n<h2 class=\"Tag\" id=\"AlertsNotificationHeading\">Alerts In Effect</h2>\n<button aria-label=\"Dismiss\" class=\"AlertsNotification__DismissButton\" type=\"button\">\nDismiss\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#close\"></use>\n</svg>\n</button>\n<span class=\"hr clearfix\"></span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__Body\" id=\"AlertsNotificationBody\">\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__MoreLinkContainer\">\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#add\"></use>\n</svg>\n<a class=\"AlertsNotification__MoreLink\" href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/conditions.htm\" id=\"AlertsNotificationMoreLink\" tabindex=\"-1\">\nmore information on current conditions...\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"MainContent\" id=\"main\" role=\"main\">\n\n<div aria-labelledby=\"modal-contact-us-label\" class=\"modal fade\" id=\"modal-contact-us\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"modal-dialog\">\n<div class=\"modal-content\">\n<div class=\"modal-header\">\n<h4 class=\"modal-title visually-hidden\" id=\"modal-contact-us-label\">Contact Us</h4>\n<button aria-label=\"Close\" class=\"btn-close\" data-bs-dismiss=\"modal\" type=\"button\"></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"modal-body\">\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"adminTools\"></div>\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"ColumnGrid row\">\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n<div class=\"container\">\n\n</div>\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<div class=\"ColumnMain col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"ContentHeader text-content-size\">\n<h1 class=\"page-title\">Natural Sounds</h1>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Layout\" id=\"cs_control_2\"><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"CS_Layout_Table\" id=\"cs_idLayout2\" summary=\"\" width=\"100%\"><tr class=\"CS_Layout_TR\"><td class=\"CS_Layout_TD\" id=\"cs_idCell2x1x1\">\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_1962740\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<p align=\"center\"><big><em><big>\"Mountains of music swell in the river,<br/>\nHills of music billow in the creeks...<br/>\nWhile other melodies are heard<br/>\nIn the gorges of the lateral canyons.<br/>\nThe Grand Canyon is a land of song.\"</big><br/>\n</em><br/>\n- John Wesley Powell<br/>\n</big></p>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_1964674\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_1964674\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\nNatural sounds are an important part of Grand Canyon National Park. Rustling winds in the canyons and the rush of waters are the heartbeat and breath of some of our most valuable resources. <strong>You can create your own soundscape by playing more than one sound at the same time.</strong>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_1967607\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_1967607\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n.\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_1970969\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_1970969\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<p><strong>This page is a work in progress. Check back later for more sounds.</strong></p>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_5462123\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_5462123\"></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_5470809\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_5470809\"> \n\n<div class=\"gallery-listing-av responsiveAudio\">\n<ul class=\"gallery-content-av clearfix in-page\">\n<li>\n<div class=\"description clearfix\">\n<h3>Grand Canyon Natural Sound: Hance Creek </h3>\n<audio class=\"video-js vjs-default-skin\" controls=\"\" id=\"av_9CB5D4691DD8B71B0B772334F467A342\" preload=\"metadata\" style=\"width:100%;height:40px\">\n<source src=\"https://www.nps.gov/nps-audiovideo/legacy/mp3/imr/avElement/grca-creek.mp3\" type=\"audio/mp3\"/>\n</audio>\n\n<br/>\n<div class=\"left\">\n<div id=\"volumeDiv\"></div>\n<p>Recording of Hance Creek, flowing within the Vishnu schist above the Colorado River in Grand Canyon National Park.</p>\n</div><!-- end .left -->\n<div class=\"right\">\n</div><!-- end .right -->\n</div>\n<div id=\"transcriptWrapper\">\n<div class=\"transcript-control open\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0);\">Audio Transcript</a></div>\n<div class=\"transcript\" style=\"display: none;\"><p>The sound of water flowing in a small creek deep within the granite and schist walls of Grand Canyon.</p> <p></p></div>\n</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_5470827\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_5470827\">\n\n<div class=\"gallery-listing-av responsiveAudio\">\n<ul class=\"gallery-content-av clearfix in-page\">\n<li>\n<div class=\"description clearfix\">\n<h3>Grand Canyon Natural Sound: Bass Rapid </h3>\n<audio class=\"video-js vjs-default-skin\" controls=\"\" id=\"av_9D30CC3C1DD8B71B0B4F00CC1A481ABA\" preload=\"metadata\" style=\"width:100%;height:40px\">\n<source src=\"https://www.nps.gov/nps-audiovideo/legacy/mp3/imr/avElement/grca-rapids02.mp3\" type=\"audio/mp3\"/>\n</audio>\n\n<br/>\n<div class=\"left\">\n<div id=\"volumeDiv\"></div>\n<p>Bass Rapid (Colorado River Mile 108) is classified as a Class 3 Rapid on the Grand Canyon Scale. A boulder bar is located mid-channel. and can be passed either on the right or left.</p>\n</div><!-- end .left -->\n<div class=\"right\">\n</div><!-- end .right -->\n</div>\n<div id=\"transcriptWrapper\">\n<div class=\"transcript-control open\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0);\">Audio Transcript</a></div>\n<div class=\"transcript\" style=\"display: none;\"><p>The sound of the Colorado River rushing over rocks. In addition to the \"roar\" of the water, subtitle spashing sounds are alsio present.</p> <p></p></div>\n</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</td></tr>\n</table></div>\n</div><!-- col-sm-12 -->\n</div><!-- row -->\n</div><!-- ColumnMain col-sm-9 -->\n</div><!-- ColumnGrid row -->\n</div><!-- end container -->\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"ColumnGrid row\">\n<div class=\"ColumnMain col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-12 text-content-size text-content-style\">\n<p style=\"text-align:right;\">Last updated: April 2, 2018</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n <!-- ParkFooter -->\n<!--googleon: index-->\n\n</div><!-- end of <div main> -->\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<!-- the rest of the scripts are leftovers from before the centennial down and should be pared down where possible -->\n\n<link href=\"/common/commonspot/templates/assets/libs/colorbox/colorbox.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n\n<div class=\"modal fade\" id=\"outdated-browser\" role=\"dialog\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n</div>\n</body>",
